ext":"We are a family of four. I follow Chinku everywhere.","words":[[1,"We"],[2,"are"],[3,"a"],[4,"family"],[5,"of"],[6,"four."],[7,"I"],[8,"follow"],[9,"Chinku"],[10,"everywhere."]]},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13270/size6/7164a89cd1301d028953b0e9d213e554.jpg","text":"I have to look after Chinku. You see, I am older than him.","words":[[11,"I"],[12,"have"],[13,"to"],[14,"look"],[15,"after"],[16,"Chinku."],[17,"You"],[18,"see,"],[19,"I"],[20,"am"],[21,"older"],[22,"than"],[23,"him."]]},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13271/size6/a05d208d489ee9a4a2b6254bb1847170.jpg","text":"Sometimes Chinku is careless. It is my duty to guard the house.","words":[[24,"Sometimes"],[25,"Chinku"],[26,"is"],[27,"careless."],[28,"It"],[29,"is"],[30,"my"],[31,"duty"],[32,"to"],[33,"guard"],[34,"the"],[35,"house."]]},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13272/size6/d1ebd4cbc7b4bd325e1cc64122a8982a.jpg","text":"We do everything together. We work together.","words":[[36,"We"],[37,"do"],[38,"everything"],[39,"together."],[40,"We"],[41,"work"],[42,"together."]]},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13273/size6/206cf6c3eb07acd37906ea9e498e66f8.jpg","text":"We play together.","words":[[43,"We"],[44,"play"],[45,"together."]]},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13274/size6/1b245d88136357758a4994f6aff793e3.jpg","text":"We even share Ma’s scolding.","words":[[46,"We"],[47,"even"],[48,"share"],[49,"Ma’s"],[50,"scolding."]]},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13275/size6/085a48497e5bdfbe07d97b02a9f136eb.jpg","text":"When Chinku is at school I help Ma. I keep the crows away from the papads.","words":[[51,"When"],[52,"Chinku"],[53,"is"],[54,"at"],[55,"school"],[56,"I"],[57,"help"],[58,"Ma."],[59,"I"],[60,"keep"],[61,"the"],[62,"crows"],[63,"away"],[64,"from"],[65,"the"],[66,"papads."]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13276/size6/686a2f57337873236e69448b690622c6.jpg","text":"Today Chinku will be my teacher. At last, I will learn something new.","words":[[67,"Today"],[68,"Chinku"],[69,"will"],[70,"be"],[71,"my"],[72,"teacher."],[73,"At"],[74,"last,"],[75,"I"],[76,"will"],[77,"learn"],[78,"something"],[79,"new."]]},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13277/size6/e8ef2593732ebe3e5fbaf85e38eb324d.jpg","text":"I am a good doggy. I do not scare away cats.","words":[[80,"I"],[81,"am"],[82,"a"],[83,"good"],[84,"doggy."],[85,"I"],[86,"do"],[87,"not"],[88,"scare"],[89,"away"],[90,"cats."]]},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13278/size6/cbf1498be090c6b8557bb4b8a0a1218e.jpg","text":"Are you Chinku’s friend? Then you are my friend too.","words":[[91,"Are"],[92,"you"],[93,"Chinku’s"],[94,"friend?"],[95,"Then"],[96,"you"],[97,"are"],[98,"my"],[99,"friend"],[100,"too."]]},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13279/size6/6986491fb4095b6fc5ae10966bc82b0e.jpg","text":"Read the following action sentences. Which of these activities do you like to do?\n \nI like dancing.\n \nI like swimming.\n \nI like skipping.\n \nI like drawing.","words":[[101,"Read"],[102,"the"],[103,"following"],[104,"action"],[105,"sentences."],[106,"Which"],[107,"of"],[108,"these"],[109,"activities"],[110,"do"],[111,"you"],[112,"like"],[113,"to"],[114,"do?"],[115,"I"],[116,"like"],[117,"dancing."],[118,"I"],[119,"like"],[120,"swimming."],[121,"I"],[122,"like"],[123,"skipping."],[124,"I"],[125,"like"],[126,"drawing."]]},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13280/size6/3c141ba6e4b35f63a835c876a4a7f1a0.jpg","text":"I like cycling.\n I like climbing.\n Sometimes we say, “As faithful as a dog”. This is because a dog always stays close to its master. If it goes far away or is lost, a dog always finds its way back home.","words":[[127,"I"],[128,"like"],[129,"cycling."],[130,"I"],[131,"like"],[132,"climbing."],[133,"Sometimes"],[134,"we"],[135,"say,"],[136,"“As"],[137,"faithful"],[138,"as"],[139,"a"],[140,"dog”."],[141,"This"],[142,"is"],[143,"because"],[144,"a"],[145,"dog"],[146,"always"],[147,"stays"],[148,"close"],[149,"to"],[150,"its"],[151,"master."],[152,"If"],[153,"it"],[154,"goes"],[155,"far"],[156,"away"],[157,"or"],[158,"is"],[159,"lost,"],[160,"a"],[161,"dog"],[162,"always"],[163,"finds"],[164,"its"],[165,"way"],[166,"back"],[167,"home."]]}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":167}}